text: Doğanbey is the name of several localities in Turkey: * Doğanbey, Beyşehir, a township with its own municipality in Beyşehir, Konya Province * Doğanbey, Seferihisar, a coastal township with its own municipality in Seferihisar, İzmir Province * Doğanbey, Söke, a village in Söke, Aydın Province Furthermore, in association with Doğanbey, Seferihisar, are the following geographical names: * Doğanbey Cape (anciently Makria) * Doğanbey Island (anciently Makris)
title: Doğanbey
